<h1>Welcome to Nova Systems Inc.</h1>
<p>
<img class="right" alt="Nova Systems Inc." src="images/Bronze-green.gif" />
We are a team of engineers, technicians and support people dedicated to helping
our clients cope with industrial electronic equipment. Our primary focus is to
provide resources for designing, building and maintaining electronic control
systems for industrial machinery.
</p><p>
Nova Systems is a hands-on company. Our engineers and technicians are
available for on-site troubleshooting and repair of PLC and PC control
systems, AC and DC servo systems and Variable Frequency Drives.  The
knowledge and experience gained from the shop floor is incorporated into
the retrofit designs of existing equipment. This expertise is also
integrated into the designs for control systems on new OEM equipment.
</p>
